            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3ENahum%201%3A1-3%3A19%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nahu_1_1%22%20bk%3D%22nahu%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3ENahum%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20message%20concerning%20Nineveh%20came%20as%20a%20vision%20to%20Nahum%2C%20who%20lived%20in%20Elkosh.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nahu_1_2%22%20bk%3D%22nahu%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22subhead-sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Anger%20against%20Nineveh%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20is%20a%20jealous%20God%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Efilled%20with%20vengeance%20and%20rage.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EHe%20takes%20revenge%20on%20all%20who%20oppose%20him%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20continues%20to%20rage%20against%20his%20enemies!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nahu_1_3%22%20bk%3D%22nahu%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20is%20slow%20to%20get%20angry%2C%20but%20his%20power%20is%20great%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20he%20never%20lets%20the%20guilty%20go%20unpunished.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EHe%20displays%20his%20power%20in%20the%20whirlwind%20and%20the%20storm.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EThe%20billowing%20clouds%20are%20the%20dust%20beneath%20his%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nahu_1_4%22%20bk%3D%22nahu%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EAt%20his%20command%20the%20oceans%20dry%20up%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20the%20rivers%20disappear.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThe%20lush%20pastures%20of%20Bashan%20and%20Carmel%20fade%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20the%20green%20forests%20of%20Lebanon%20wither.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nahu_1_5%22%20bk%3D%22nahu%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EIn%20his%20presence%20the%20mountains%20quake%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20the%20hills%20melt%20away%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3Ethe%20earth%20trembles%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20its%20people%20are%20destroyed.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nahu_1_6%22%20bk%3D%22nahu%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EWho%20can%20stand%20before%20his%20fierce%20anger%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EWho%20can%20survive%20his%20burning%20fury%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EHis%20rage%20blazes%20forth%20like%20fire%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20the%20mountains%20crumble%20to%20dust%20in%20his%20presence.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nahu_1_7%22%20bk%3D%22nahu%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20is%20good%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ea%20strong%20refuge%20when%20trouble%20comes.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EHe%20is%20close%20to%20those%20who%20trust%20in%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nahu_1_8%22%20bk%3D%22nahu%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20he%20will%20sweep%20away%20his%20enemies%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E1%3A8%3C%2Fspan%3E%20As%20in%20Greek%20version%3B%20Hebrew%20reads%20%3Cem%3Esweep%20away%20her%20place.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ein%20an%20overwhelming%20flood.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EHe%20will%20pursue%20his%20foes%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Einto%20the%20darkness%20of%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nahu_1_9%22%20bk%3D%22nahu%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EWhy%20are%20you%20scheming%20against%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EHe%20will%20destroy%20you%20with%20one%20blow%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ehe%20won%26%23x2019%3Bt%20need%20to%20strike%20twice!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nahu_1_10%22%20bk%3D%22nahu%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EHis%20enemies%2C%20tangled%20like%20thornbushes%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20staggering%20like%20drunks%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewill%20be%20burned%20up%20like%20dry%20stubble%20in%20a%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nahu_1_11%22%20bk%3D%22nahu%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EWho%20is%20this%20wicked%20counselor%20of%20yours%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewho%20plots%20evil%20against%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nahu